---
title: Cozy Chicken Thighs and Pesto Orzo with Spinach and Peas
description: This drool-worthy orzo dish is creamy and luscious without being too heavy! It's made even more enticing with a hit of fragrant basil pesto bringing herbaceous goodness and green veggies adding some balance. A zesty-garlic seasoned chicken thigh is perfect to top it all off.
